      }, this), "### John He is the writer - the Scribe ### The Father \"Which is, which was, and which is to come.\" ### The Spirit \"From the seven Spirits which are before His throne;\" SEVEN: \"Hepta\" - signifying to be full - \"Pneuma\" \"Spirit\" . Therefore, meaning: a \"Seven-fold spirit\". God is described here in the fullness of His office and powers. ### The Son \"And from Jesus Christ, who is the faithful witness, and the first begotten of the dead, and the prince of the kings of the earth.\"", /*#__PURE__*/_jsxDEV("h3", {
